  "text": "For fuzzy weighted association rule mining standard ARM algorithms can be used or at least adopted after some modifications. The Improved Fuzzy Weighted ARM algorithm belongs to the breadth first traversal family of ARM algorithms, developed using tree data structures and works in a fashion similar to the Apriori algorithm [CITATION_1] .",
